  "prompt": "Which is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center in Calhoun County AL?",
  "response": "Finding a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center in Calhoun County, AL, can depend on various factors including the specific needs of the individual, the severity of the addiction, and any co-occurring mental health issues. Here are a few options that may be worth considering:\n\n1. **Bradford Health Services - Oxford**: Located close to Calhoun County, Bradford Health Services provides comprehensive inpatient treatment programs including detox, individual counseling, and group therapy.\n\n2. **New Beginnings Recovery**: Although not specifically in Calhoun County, it is a nearby option that offers inpatient detox and rehabilitation services.\n\n3. **The Bridge, Inc.**: This facility offers inpatient substance abuse treatment and is known for its holistic approach to recovery.\n\n4. **Anniston Fellowship House**: Located in Anniston, AL, this facility offers residential treatment services for those struggling with addiction.\n\n5. **Highland Health Systems**: They provide a range of services including inpatient rehabilitation for substance abuse.\n\nIt's important to contact these facilities directly to learn more about their treatment programs, availability, insurance coverage, and admission requirements. Additionally, consulting with a healthcare professional can help in making an informed decision about the best rehab center for your needs.",
